  "text": "The first biochemical, negative feedback oscillator model reported-the Goodwin oscillator-contains three interconnected components with specific production and degradation rates [CITATION_1] . Since then, a growing amount of more complex and more close-to-biology models was established as indicated above, which comprises more genes and explain subtle experimental observations.",
